# Un-ignore shared plugin settings — committed as part of the plugin
!.claude/
!.claude/settings.json

# Un-ignore CLAUDE.md — it's part of the plugin
!CLAUDE.md

# Keep local/personal Claude settings out of the repo
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/flow-states/

